Package: sparseHiC
Type: Package
Title: Efficient compression and analysis of Hi-C Data
Version: 0.4.1
Date: 2016-09-29
Authors@R: c(
    person("Caleb", "Lareau", email = "caleblareau@g.harvard.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Martin", "Aryee", email = "aryee.martin@mgh.harvard.edu", role = "aut")
    )
Maintainer: Caleb Lareau <caleblareau@g.harvard.edu>
Author: Caleb Lareau [aut, cre], Martin Aryee [aut]
Description: A set of functions to compress output from common
    Hi-C pre-processing tools and transforming them into efficient
    sparse matrices for further downstream analyses, including visualization, 
    library normalization, differential boundary calls, etc. 
Imports:
